name: Bioforge Darius
description: To save his own life after being exposed to a cloud of radioactive space gas, investment banker Donald D. Darius was forced to build a suit containing the strange mixture. But the chemicals from beyond the stars warped his weakened mind, twisting him into the brutal villain known as Bioforge!
